metadata.name: Canimals - OZ
metadata.description:
Canimals #1 - OZ

Canimals are modern day urban pixies - mischievous, adventurous and inquisitive.
They love to play and create innocent mayhem.

Canimals can roll, stack and literally POP up anywhere.

Canimals appear and act up when you’re not looking! Just like kids their age they play and share, squabble and explore, and sometimes things get out of hand.
Humans discover that someone or something has been up to mischief, but they never find out who’s responsible.

Canimals are already here but you may not have seen them?

In recognition of its novel materials and high-quality expression techniques,
Canimals ranked second among more than 1,000 works in Mipcom Junior, France, in 2009,
and was selected as the best animation chosen by children
at the same venue the following year. 

It also won the 2011 Korea Content Awards and the Character Presidential Award.
